{"tid":1633875,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"檢討尋日鵝頸橋一役(行動檢討)","createTime":"2019-10-07T05:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T05:49:02.000Z","uid":67292,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2d869faeccb4d45bdc4ab0d6fe9c8375a9a77505","tid":1633875,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:34:52.000Z","msg":"尋日有經歷鵝頸橋一役既人，可能大多數人會認為輸在後排手足企太密，導致防暴衝擊既時候無位走，令到有一大批人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n但其實我在前線觀察，除左後排企太密，資訊唔夠流通，仲有幾個死症。<br />\n<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>過份迷戀對峙</strong></span></span><br />\n係啊，又係對峙，在油站對出前線起碼同狗對峙左半個鐘。呢半個鐘既無人進攻，又無人退後。無錯，你眼前見到D防暴無向前推進，但咁樣係咪等於無危險呢？絕對唔係，狗同我地唔一樣，佢地有完整既指揮體系，當你見到前線防暴唔推進，只有兩種可能性：第一，佢地等緊<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">增援</span></span>，再<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">進攻</span></span>。第二，佢地準備緊<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">包圍</span></span>。所以係同一位置拖<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">越耐</span>，只會越<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不利</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n檢討：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔夠打就走</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">唔撚好係到扮型拖時間</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，你拖個個陪你拖，最後被捕既就係走得慢既手足。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>以為人力可以阻擋警察衝鋒</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尋日點解會被警察大追殺，因為大家都以為人多就可以對抗警察。但事實係相反，人多反而令到個戰術機動性弱，警察一衝就會心理恐慌而全線崩潰。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">無可靠路障</span></span>更加係死症，警察完全無阻擋，亦都無時間比遠攻輸出，結果警察可以直接衝入人群。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n檢討：<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔好守無路障或者無物資整路障既地方</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。如果路障被拆或者被迫退就一路退到見唔到警察再起路障。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>過份高估火魔法的力量</strong></span></span><br />\n火魔法睇落雖然好威猛，但我幾次前線既觀察，火魔法有幾個問題。<br />\n第一，火魔法實際傷害係有限<br />\n以中火魔法既便衣警為例，中晒成支都無事，你可能會話可能係果位火魔法師等級低。但同樣，防暴既綠衫係有火抗功能，基本上好難實際傷害到佢地，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">警察亦都漸漸發現呢樣野</span></span>。重點係，好多手足仍然覺得火魔法可以阻擋警察，甚至可以燒水砲車。結果水砲車已到，大家仲係到望下望下，導致大敗。<br />\n第二，火魔法極易TK<br />\n有高級魔法師射程遠準確度高，值得讚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但亦有好多新手亂黎，今次掉中記者無大事，但難保唔會有一日出事。我自己係前線唔只一次差D被TK，所以希望火魔法師們真係要<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">慎用</span></span></strong>火魔法，如果掉記者或者FA就死。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n檢討：<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">無路障就退，唔好以為火魔法係萬能，更加唔好覺得火魔法可以有效阻擋警察。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n尋日因為呢場大敗拉左好多個15歲都唔夠既妹妹弟弟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家真係認真反思戰術問題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aea9978121e6bb8b6abfa321fbbd4375492af2e6","tid":1633875,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:34:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88ddca3469c031ceff1fac361de60cd54d38b314","tid":1633875,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:35:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e68683057a0c58da1aaf4a9a16e424f011700341","tid":1633875,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:35:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d22ba0b575efa7f3a2dc26d2289100ebe7984803","tid":1633875,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:36:50.000Z","msg":"個夢咁真"},{"pid":"47a3eb839cd401d6083161345eb4e43c8c29c4ba","tid":1633875,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:36:51.000Z","msg":"認同既朋友幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c04e345431a822d304be7d82118f2d841f231882","tid":1633875,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d22ba0b575efa7f3a2dc26d2289100ebe7984803","tid":1633875,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:36:50.000Z","msg":"個夢咁真"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:38:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：我睇直播，好似好多現場直播。"},{"pid":"60ab737bd08f12f35371aaaca36e1ab01107da2b","tid":1633875,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:42:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a8a078b47a9af5ef0323cd5c1914d51fadaae2d","tid":1633875,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:49:02.000Z","msg":"無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}